# Dotfiles-local

Dependencies:
* zsh (as late as possible; >4.3.10 misses a lot of features)
* vim (latest and greatest with python support)
* tmux (latest and greatest for best results)

Optional dependecies:
* yaourt (https://archlinux.fr/yaourt-en)
```
yaourt -S acpi dmenu unclutter xlockmore twmn-git rxvt-unicode pulseaudio pulseaudio-alsa pulseaudio-ctl xorg-xbacklight pm-utils firefox flashplugin chromium chromium-pepper-flash xorg-server xorg-server-utils i3-wm ttf-inconsolata terminus-font feh --noconfirm
```

Installation:
Pull, go nuts with symlinks. ...or do something more elegant with, say, puppet, salt, or ansible...
